  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售业务流程图，核心是会员忠诚度和销售终端这两个模块。我想把Retail_CustomerLoyalty和Retail_PointOfSale作为关键节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Retail_CustomerLoyalty我理解为Audit节点，Retail_PointOfSale对应Bail节点。除了这两个，订单管理Retail_OrderManagement需要加入吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，订单管理拆成两个节点：Code和Define。另外会员忠诚度其实有两个实例，一个叫Audit，另一个叫Barg，分别处理不同的业务场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加五个节点：Audit、Bail、Barg、Code、Define。现在我来梳理连接关系，Audit应该指向Define，表示忠诚度数据流入订单管理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，还有Bail和Barg之间是双向的，销售终端和会员系统互相调用。另外Code到Define是顺序流转，订单创建后进入定义阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接Bail<-Barg双向箭头，以及Code--Define。Define还要连到Barg吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Define到Barg，订单完成后更新会员积分。另外还需要两个中间节点：Risk和Signal，处理风控和信号流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Risk和Signal已添加。Risk指向Signal，Signal再连到Barg，形成风控链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还差一个Place节点，代表支付环节，它通过Press动作触发后续流程。Place单独存在，不直接连到其他业务节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Place--Press是一条带标签的边，Place是独立节点。目前结构：五个业务节点加两个中间节点Risk、Signal，以及Place。流向都正确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了，Barg和Bail的双向关系，箭头方向让我再确认——应该是Barg指向Bail，同时Bail也指向Barg，没错。但Define到Barg的箭头方向我刚才反了，应该是Define指向Barg。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，Define--Barg方向确认无误。所有节点和连接：Audit--Define, Code--Define, Define--Barg, Bail<--Barg, Risk--Signal, Signal--Barg, Place--Press。还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Code",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
